{
  "stem": "11175.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They dig them and put them in-- in the machine, the-- Like he was-- I-- I-- I saw-- I saw recently, from Bosnia, the-- the-- you know, [STAMMERING] grabbing the machine, grabbing the-- all the deads and putting them in a grave.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what's-- that's what's happened there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let me tell you that our camp was also prepared for an uprising.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We organized themself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were-- the day-- the day when they liquidated-- liquidated our camp, the day when they took out everybody to be shot, this morning supposed to be an uprising in our camp.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was  a rumor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, there was one guy there, which he tipped off the SS that the Jews, they're going to make an uprising there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a rumor-- the same day was that the rumor, because in the same day, they liquidated the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's because the Russian Army, maybe, advanced.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[STAMMERING] The rumor was then [STAMMERING] one guy-- we knew that guy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They said it's Froim Rikner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And [STAMMERS] the other guy, this was not [STAMMERS] they accused him not the right way, because this is Ignac.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was-- he was a kapo there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he did not do the-- as a matter of fact, they pointed at him also that he was also from the organizers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took him out, and they shot him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, Rikner, he-- after the liquidation from the ghetto, from that camp, from Treblinka, where we-- where I was-- I'm not talking about the Treblinka from there-- so that SS, I heard, I found out from one guy, which he was also in Treblinka, and he also ran away.",
      "word_count": 50
    }
  ],
